  "description": "Registry of government schemes, programmes, missions, and funds. IDs are permanently stable. active=false + archived=true for historical resolution of dissolved schemes. v1.0: sector field now references FUNC-* IDs from registry_entities.json function_vocabulary (was free string). administering_entity_id validated against registry_entities.json (pipeline enforced). legislation field now uses legislation_code format e.g. ACT-NREGA-2005 for machine-resolveability.",
